{"tid":1638663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黨鐵扮壞封左出閘口","createTime":"2019-10-08T11:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T16:54:58.000Z","uid":31065,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"85d3c83c6132cd3f212199364f5ca547c5fae99d","tid":1638663,"uid":31065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:29:12.000Z","msg":"頭先係九龍灣站出閘，咁黨鐵就封左好多個出閘位話壞機啦，咁我就試下用其中一部壞機出閘啦，屌佢老母，嘟一聲勁清楚，跟手我試下拍另一部出閘機，咁當然係出唔到啦，跟手梗係去詢問處問下啦，佢既回覆答已經扣左錢，仲好意思講係咁架因為我地好多機壞左<br />\n屌佢老母，係壞左定扮壞左呀，黨鐵真係好可耿，扮壞去屈鳩人破壞佢d設施<br />\n排隊出入閘既人不妨幫手試下佢係咪真係壞左，唔洗晒時間係度鳩排<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQ3KOeZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQ3KOeZ.jpg&h=3fae5789&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1f3d55d1d4c9b3ae9a4c4891689217ed791a7a8","tid":1638663,"uid":31065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:30:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff78c112ad73ebdd22b9c0bdb52d38ba4b5780b8","tid":1638663,"uid":154470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:30:43.000Z","msg":"個欄推到？"},{"pid":"ce7e7e9b4ff82af35bc0886cf85b5769a398dbfc","tid":1638663,"uid":31065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:31:49.000Z","msg":"推到丫"},{"pid":"32208bfc8ef2a7eb17b60768c94deef27cfc2c63","tid":1638663,"uid":5258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:32:00.000Z","msg":"推 好心啲人直接跳啦"},{"pid":"5fce62b55489b8361f17adffa7ca98c8ebe8aa81","tid":1638663,"uid":8647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:32:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c9060b77917275b4f00bc094de7b7540b6dcc37","tid":1638663,"uid":30990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:33:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4d547ef3ec72c4f9aa19f707f6b2ecf804207b6","tid":1638663,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim